 * [Download Opera Webconverger](http://download.webconverger.com/opera/)

Opera is run in a kiosk mode. These settings are set by the **webconverger-base** package and they need some work:

    ; Put any settings here that are not overridable by users
    [User Prefs]
    Browser JavaScript=1
    Enable Wand=0
    Enable Gesture=0
    No Local File=1
    [State]
    Accept License=1
    [Install]
    One Time Page=""
    [Special]
    Go Home Time Out=60
    Home URL=http://portal.webconverger.com


`/usr/bin/opera -k -noprint -kioskresetstation -kioskwindows -nomenu -nohotlist -resetonexit -nosave -e $GO`



